Package: iChip
Title: Bayesian Modeling of ChIP-chip Data Through Hidden Ising Models
Version: 1.9.1
Date: 2011-4-8
Depends: R (>= 2.10.0)
Imports: limma
Author: Qianxing Mo
Maintainer: Qianxing Mo  <moq@mskcc.org>
Description: This package uses hidden Ising models to identify enriched genomic
             regions in ChIP-chip data.  It can be used to analyze the data
             from multiple platforms (e.g., Affymetrix, Agilent, and NimbleGen),
             and the data with single to multiple replicates. 
LazyData: yes
License: GPL (>= 2)
biocViews: ChIP-chip, NimbleGen, Microarray, Bioinformatics
